{"tid":1975165,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全球首宗屍傳人 泰法醫病歿","createTime":"2020-04-16T10:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T14:00:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7e654a9f45cb7e7013dcfe934f281b92af506f24","tid":1975165,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:53:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200416/XQ5VDYTZCHFO3AUNH2YHL63ZXA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200416%2FXQ5VDYTZCHFO3AUNH2YHL63ZXA%2F&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10GFzq3Uwi%2FWN07E9MureYdc%3D&h=1521c14f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200416%2FXQ5VDYTZCHFO3AUNH2YHL63ZXA%2F&h=35e9c4aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200416/XQ5VDYTZCHFO3AUNH2YHL63ZXA/</a><br />\n<br />\n全球首宗屍傳人 泰法醫病歿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200416/large/1586966579_a97a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200416%2Flarge%2F1586966579_a97a.gif&h=cfe5afa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在曼谷一家醫院外，醫護人員設立攤位為駕駛者採樣檢測。<br />\n<br />\n泰國上月出現相信是全球首宗屍體傳人的武漢肺炎病例，曼谷一名法醫從屍體接觸病毒受感染後死亡。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：發展中國家勢受衝擊<br />\n<br />\n專家促殯儀業留神<br />\n<br />\n曼谷RVT醫療中心的斯里維吉塔萊（Won Sriwijitalai）和印度孟買帕提爾大學（DY Patil University）的威萬尼基特（Viroj Wiwanitkit）上月20日去信《鑑識與法醫學期刊》指，今次是首宗法醫人員感染武漢肺炎死亡的個案。法醫染疫時當地的確診案例有272宗，大部份為境外輸入，病毒尚未在境內擴散，與他同期感染的還有一名護士。<br />\n<br />\n二人在信中指，「法醫透過接觸確診患者而染疫的機會微，但他們與生物樣本和屍體會有接觸。在泰國，檢驗屍體是否帶有武漢肺炎病毒並非慣常做法，故目前並無確實數據顯示泰國有多少屍體具有武漢肺炎病毒。不過有必要在這方面做防控工作」。<br />\n<br />\n他們建議法醫人員工作時穿着防護裝備，包括保護衣、手套、護目鏡、面罩和口罩；病理學和法醫學部門處理屍體時必須跟隨手術室的消毒程序。專家就提醒不只是法醫，在停屍間和殯儀館工作的人都應留神，更甚者任何人接觸「無論是生或死」的確診患者的都應穿着防護裝備。<br />\n<br />\n不過，世界衞生組織（WHO）上月底就如何安全處理武肺患者屍體的指引中指，除了伊波拉出血熱和馬堡出血熱外，屍體一般不具傳染性。<br />\n<br />\n美國《新聞周刊》"},{"pid":"6973eec863b281281acc080d657a6f7733fcc740","tid":1975165,"uid":17628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:59:17.000Z","msg":"屍戰泰國"},{"pid":"68496d8188a52dc5a99d540d5a3b2062c8cda31e","tid":1975165,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T11:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc21f258b77c7894b295eff134a8d323482d156","tid":1975165,"uid":54126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T11:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7bca5ef2edc1472d90a1df85151647396118f2","tid":1975165,"uid":292497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T11:05:26.000Z","msg":"升左壞疽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90542a6a371b03cb0f5847d557b09693c0c2c817","tid":1975165,"uid":65834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T11:07:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0492360ac8592ea59aefae31457751ed6b0a5744","tid":1975165,"uid":99700,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T11:07:59.000Z","msg":"滅絕屍泰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b982ee6d4e8706638cf0624d0b47b3f3a1c638","tid":197